+ * Same goes for 5212 who has xr/a/b/g support (total 28 rates).
+ * First comes the XR table, then 802.11a, 802.11b and 802.11g.
+ * When hw returns eg. 27 it points to the last 802.11g rate (54Mbits) etc
+ */
