+/************************** EEPROM BANDS ****************************
+ *
+ * The iwl_eeprom_band definitions below provide the mapping from the
+ * EEPROM contents to the specific channel number supported for each
+ * band.
+ *
+ * For example, iwl_priv->eeprom.band_3_channels[4] from the band_3
